	installation:
	* hostname bugfix

version 4.0.1 (01/29/2009):
	frontend:
	* better RSS feed
	* variable title
	* redirect from old post URLs (NORS 3) to new URLs
	* save commentator's credentials to cookie
	* bug fixes

	administration:
	* clear all HTML in items list

	core:
